   - Highlight my name in accent color.

3. Projects Page:
   - Grid layout displaying at least 3 project cards.
   - Each card includes a category/meta tag, project title, and short description.

4. Blog Page:
   - Grid layout displaying at least 3 blog cards.
   - Each card includes category/meta tag, blog title, and short description.

5. Footer or header social buttons:
   - Include standard social buttons (e.g., GitHub, LinkedIn) in a consistent style.
